<head>大正 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0925001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0925001">前頁[02]不分卷【甲】</note>
<note n="0925002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0925002">這＝遮【宮】【甲】下同</note>
<note n="0926001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0926001">鑪＝驢【宮】，爐【甲】</note>
<note n="0926002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0926002">泰＝秦【甲】</note>
<note n="0927001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0927001">以＝謂【甲】</note>
<note n="0927002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0927002">何如＝如何【甲】</note>
<note n="0927003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0927003">正＋（當）【甲】</note>
<note n="0927004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0927004">是＝此【甲】</note>
<note n="0929001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0929001">大慧普覺禪師書上終【甲】</note>
<note n="0929002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0929002">大慧普覺禪師書下首，參學惠然錄【甲】</note>
<note n="0929003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0929003">棙＝捩【宮】【甲】＊</note>
<note n="0930001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0930001">不分卷【甲】</note>
